## Required GEE Assets

The following assets are required to run these scripts. Assets
marked [PRIVATE] are not publicly shared. Contact the
corresponding author (m.hafizt@uq.edu.au) for access or
substitute with your own equivalent data.

### Training data

| Asset | Description | Availability |
|-------|-------------|--------------|
| combined_dataSP_all_years_with_S2_clean | Field survey observations (2018-2022) with seagrass percent cover and species composition | [PRIVATE] Available upon request subject to BRIN governance |

### Study area boundaries

| Asset | Description | Availability |
|-------|-------------|--------------|
| R2_case_study | FeatureCollection of five study site boundaries with loc property | [PRIVATE] |

### Environmental layers

| Asset | Description | Availability |
|-------|-------------|--------------|
| raster_INA_ACA_Bathymetry | Shallow water bathymetry (Allen Coral Atlas) | [PRIVATE] - Original source: https://allencoralatlas.org |
