## Notes on Module Dependencies

Scripts in this repository are self-contained and do not
depend on external GEE modules.

The original development version used shared GEE modules
(mosaic_classification_functions_Indo and seagrass_params_Indo)
developed in collaboration with the Marine Remote Sensing Group
at the University of Queensland. Only the functions and
parameters relevant to this study have been extracted and
included inline in the published scripts.
